				<td colspan="2"><span>Tonight I get this tell...
<br />
&quot;what level is our first ae sv song?&quot;
<br />
I figure this is a semi low level bard being harrased, so I reply, &quot;54&quot;
<br />
The person responds, &quot;thanks&quot;
<br />

<br />
Now I get a burr up my hide and /who all temluen (spelling might be wrong) and get back that this is a level 65 Bard asking me this now foolish question.
<br />

<br />
For petes sake, and anyone else starting with a p, if you are that level why are you asking me that kind of question?
<br />
My answer is that you are ebayed and no longer worth any of my tiime.  Welcome to /ignore.  Should you happen to come upon these forums and be reading about yourself I would hope that you would take some time to go read about the class of character you just spent way too much IRL money on and learn how to play it.  Else you will wind up in the tomes of those that give us bad names.
<br />

<br />
Ok end of rant, back to finding that purrrfect pillow upon which to lay my tired bod.</span></td>
